- The integer 2D array parameter `grid` must not be null.
- The integer result is the total surface area of the resulting shapes after gluing adjacent cubes.
- The integer result is greater than or equal to 0.
- The integer result is less than or equal to 2500.
- The length of the integer 2D array parameter `grid` is equal to the length of each sub-array within `grid`.
- The length of the integer 2D array parameter `grid` is greater than or equal to 1.
- The length of the integer 2D array parameter `grid` is less than or equal to 50.
- All values in the integer 2D array parameter `grid` are greater than or equal to 0.
- All values in the integer 2D array parameter `grid` are less than or equal to 50.